OL,3,C'Nothing can undo it': Teenager speaks
OL,4,Cout after being sexually assaulted
OL,6,FA Guernsey teenager who was sexually
OL,7,Fassaulted says "nothing can undo the
OL,8,Fharm that was caused".
OL,10,FIn a joint statement with her family,
OL,11,Fwhich has been released by the
OL,12,Fisland's police force, they say the
OL,13,Fimpact on them is "difficult to put
OL,14,Finto words".
