OL,3,C'Nothing can undo it': Teenager speaks
OL,4,Cout after being sexually assaulted
OL,6,FJacob Brady, 23, was jailed for four
OL,7,Fyears and four months by Guernsey's
OL,8,FRoyal Court on Wednesday (25 February)
OL,9,Fafter admitting sexually touching the
OL,10,Fteenage girl, who was aged 14 at the
OL,11,Ftime, and possessing indecent images
OL,12,Fof children.
OL,14,FBrady befriended the teenager and
OL,15,Ftexted her regularly before
OL,16,Fintentionally touching her sexually
OL,17,Fwithout her consent inside his car.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
