OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772223642
OL,3,C'Nothing can undo it': Teenager speaks
OL,4,Cout after being sexually assaulted
OL,6,FThe assault was reported and following
OL,7,FBrady's arrest, 26 indecent images of
OL,8,Fchildren were found by officers on his
OL,9,Fdevices.
OL,11,FGuernsey Police adds: "We cannot
OL,12,Foverstate how abhorrent offences of
OL,13,Fthis nature are. They can have a
OL,14,Flifelong impact on victims.
OL,16,F"We would like to commend the victim
OL,17,Fin this case for their bravery in
OL,18,Fcoming forward, and for working with
OL,19,Fdetectives during the investigation."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
