OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772223642
OL,3,C'Nothing can undo it': Teenager speaks
OL,4,Cout after being sexually assaulted
OL,6,FThe teenage victim's family says: "The
OL,7,Fimpact of this abuse on our daughter's
OL,8,Fmental health has been profound and
OL,9,Flong-lasting.
OL,11,F"We continue to support her as she
OL,12,Frebuilds her sense of safety,
OL,13,Fconfidence and wellbeing.
OL,15,F"While today is about accountability,
OL,16,Fwe also hope that the perpetrator uses
OL,17,Fhis time in custody to reflect on the
OL,18,Fharm he has caused and to engage with
OL,19,Fany support offered to him, so that he
OL,20,Fcan rehabilitate and rebuild his life
OL,21,Fafter serving his sentence.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
