PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772223642
OL,3,C'Nothing can undo it': Teenager speaks
OL,4,Cout after being sexually assaulted
OL,6,F"We want to send a clear message to
OL,7,Fother victims of sexual crime in
OL,8,FGuernsey: you are not alone, and you
OL,9,Fshould not be afraid to come forward.
OL,11,F"Support is available, you will be
OL,12,Flistened to, and you will be treated
OL,13,Fwith care, dignity and respect."
OL,15,FThe family thanks Guernsey Police, the
OL,16,FReparative Care Team and the Victim
OL,17,FSupport and Witness Service, stating
OL,18,Fthat "their support has made a
OL,19,Fmeaningful difference to our
OL,20,Fdaughter's ability to cope and to seek
OL,21,Fjustice".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
